			<action-date date="20140605">June 5, 2014</action-date>
			<action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="S312">Mrs. McCaskill</sponsor> (for herself, <cosponsor name-id="S212">Mr. Coats</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="S182">Ms. Mikulski</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="S314">Mr. Tester</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="S252">Ms. Collins</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the Select Committee on
			 Intelligence</action-desc>
